## Maintenance (MANDATORY)

When creating a new agent or modifying an existing one in `.claude/agents/`:

1. **This file** (`.cursor/rules/agents.mdc`) -- update the Agent Registry table, coordination flow, patterns, and file list
2. **`CLAUDE.md`** (Agent System section) -- update the agent list and any affected guidance
3. **Coordination flow** -- if the new/changed agent introduces or alters inter-agent relationships, update the ASCII diagram and Key Coordination Patterns above
